Package graph.api

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Edge
    Represents the directed link between two Node objects and may contain and optional weight.
    Graph
    Root data structure that may contain N or more Nodes connected by a series of edges.
    Node<T,U extends java.lang.Comparable<?>>
    Represents the core data structure that will make up the main Graph component.
